Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:35.94,Ep Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Two Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:42.36,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You have 24 hours until \Nthe beam cannon fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.40,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If your decision comes too late,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:48.93,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow will be remembered \Nin the history of space as
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:53.17,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,the day the star wars began, \Na day that will live in infamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:02:00.31,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,And the first act of war will be to \Nreduce Earth, the catalyst, to space dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:08.39,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,It would be unwise to attempt to search \Nthis large planet for our present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:12.46,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,There is an emergency defense \Nsystem built into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.19,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,If you try anything funny, \Nthis planet will be destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.15,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,before the beam cannon ever fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:23.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did that guy come back \Nto destroy his home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:30.28,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,As a planet, Beam and its population are \Nbasically one big weapons manufacturer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.42,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,But as a nation, they're too smart \Nto butt into interstellar politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:40.94,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,However, there's a group called the \NFirestarters who pulls strings to start wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:44.50,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,The Galaxy Sword Master \Nhas made his name through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:46.08,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,his exploits in those wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:49.00,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,But if he is, in truth, a fictitious hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.70,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,whose purpose is to start those wars...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:54.72,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:57.01,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:57.94,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.39,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:08.50,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shin-bo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.70,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, I'm doing fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.12,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's such a lovely morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:16.09,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Edo mornings are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.71,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.93,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go for a jog like we used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:31.77,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't realize \Nthat he's being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,How do we stop the mechanical \Nhalf of his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:42.39,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something Shinpachi \Nor Otae can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:49.34,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we will now chase down the \Ninterstellar wave beam cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:52.00,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Grab every person who looks suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:55.29,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san, what would \Nbe a suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:58.92,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who looks like he \Nmight shoot out beams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.33,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this guy's shooting \Nidiot beams from his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.22,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Throw him in the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:05.15,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.74,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to murder you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.83,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kondo-san! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.52,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:12.77,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who looks like he \Nmight shoot out beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.04,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is the worst threat \Nthe nation has faced since
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.52,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the founding of the Tokugawa Bakufu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:21.13,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,The Yagyu must step up to \Nscore points with the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.36,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.99,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Step up to protect Edo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.94,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,More paper money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.83,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Complete our celebrity blockade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:31.83,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who included Takagi \NBoo with the celebrities?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:34.66,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say to use \Na Drifters blockade?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:36.83,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said to use a celebrity \Nblockade, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.11,0:04:40.68,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I should look \Nfor women who are easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:43.22,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would be a **** blockade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.22,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.81,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.89,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know since I've \Nnever done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.64,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Temperature's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.23,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very hamnida!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.21,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Care to join me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.21,0:04:57.36,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to kill you, \NPervy Sword Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:02.96,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,A bath really hits the \Nspot after some sparring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.20,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Shin-bo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.61,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.75,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You need to scorch your delicate \Nspots to make them squeaky clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of gunk did you \Npick up out in space?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:23.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Still, where is he hiding \Nthe beam cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.88,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,All I can see is a little pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.39,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Gin-guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.27,0:05:35.52,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,If you stab him with this blade I've \Nrigged with a disruption device,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:39.02,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,it will delay the activation of \Nthe emergency defense system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.98,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,That will be your chance to destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.97,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the mechanical half of his \Nbody and fully disable him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.03,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the \Nhuman side of his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:48.69,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,I already gave you an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.39,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,That machine is keeping \Nhim alive right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.39,0:05:58.50,Main01,Gen,0000,0000,0000,,If the machine is disabled, the human half \Nof his body will go back to being dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:04.49,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:15.64,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you carrying \Nthat weapon, Gin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:18.13,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.15,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to cut down your first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.15,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,You're not trying to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Half-assed lies don't work on women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are puffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:35.16,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:40.64,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.25,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I could barely feel you \Nscrubbing my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.35,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You've really grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.26,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Though you haven't changed down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:49.80,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.29,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're still out of my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:07:01.47,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-bo, you're already \Nstronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:06.30,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,All I got for leaving Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:12.79,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,was this beat-up body and the \Nhollow title of Sword Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:18.89,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,After returning to Edo and seeing \Nyou guys, I realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:24.42,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't find something \Nclose to protect,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:29.17,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,you can wander the entire universe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:30.94,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,and never achieve true strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:38.35,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I should have returned sooner to \Nthe country of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.98,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it sound like you've given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can work together \Nto find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.42,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,We can work together to become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.76,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,So don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:03.47,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Our Hajime-nii would \Nnever look so defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:15.97,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-bo, so you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:19.61,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:24.02,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,So please, we won't ask \Nyou to wait until tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.79,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,but could you give us \Na little more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:29.19,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please lower your sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:31.44,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:39.54,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to introduce \Nyou and Gin-san to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.40,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I always hoped that one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:45.28,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,the two of you would sit \Nhere next to each other
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:49.59,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,while I washed your backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:50.70,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:53.59,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.35,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:02.55,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, Gin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.08,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Just give us a little more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.60,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Let him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.69,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,be Shin-chan's big brother \Na little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.37,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to restrain the \Nother half of my body much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.31,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared to end my own life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:24.04,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,but I came back to Edo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:29.36,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,because I wanted to see you \Nand Otae-chan one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:34.29,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Soz about getting you \Ninto all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:41.31,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I got to see this \Ncity of samurai one last time—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:48.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you all have those \Nlooks on your faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:57.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what the \NSchool of Beam Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.66,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,teaches about reacting \Nin these situations?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:03.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Instructor Obi-one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.16,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.22,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.13,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.60,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.41,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.52,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Shinpachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.52,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:31.06,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.33,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.30,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:36.74,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you be so cruel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.50,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-nii knows everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:41.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He understands what's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.74,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,He's prepared to end his own life!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not his body anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:59.05,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You were washing a dead body \Nwith some junk attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:02.80,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.85,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to repeat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.11,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.63,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop this, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:15.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm not interested \Nin sitting around with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.74,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,a bunch of emotional saps, \Nwaiting for my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't handle the job, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.24,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.90,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:36.34,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I said to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.51,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you deaf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.57,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.02,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,How can two big brothers \Nbe so different?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the face of a big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:00.65,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,True, your nose hairs are sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:04.22,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.26,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:08.86,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:13.36,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.17,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency defense \Nsystem hasn't activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.88,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,That man must have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:27.10,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Was he able to sense my \Nintention to kill that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:28.56,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.10,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:36.23,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.15,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,He can shoot beams from his eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.46,0:12:39.41,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.41,0:12:40.44,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,We can't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.16,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.73,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,You better find him before \NI finish smoking this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:55.67,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Shah that guy up before these curtain \Nrings can "shah" the curtain shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:57.69,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Or else it's seppuku time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:01.45,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,You middle management people are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.81,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:05.50,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you go if you \Ntell us where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:07.26,Main01,Kag,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.26,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.27,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Shin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:13.28,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's up in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:16.06,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so intent on \Ndestroying Hajime-nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.36,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this gives \NKondo-san and Kyubei-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.92,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,an excuse to rid themselves of their rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.03,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That's despicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.71,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You're all despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.75,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Not as despicable as your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.88,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, this is Kenofi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:43.64,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.40,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I request assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.88,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,My current coordinates are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:56.94,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't spurred into action \Nby my lady or Kondo-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:03.81,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,It was your leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:06.89,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,This was a mistake on my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:09.05,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect him to have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.69,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,such a dangerous man as \Nhis new brother figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all so obsessed \Nwith the brother thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:23.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Shinpachi nor I am \Ninterested in being brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:25.09,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Gin-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.09,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:31.75,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the news has gotten out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.89,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we can't let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.57,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinsengumi are on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.90,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:41.15,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,We will search every nook \Nand cranny of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.85,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,You should go take a bath and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,wash every nook and cranny of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:46.96,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wh-Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:48.31,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't here to capture Obi-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:51.32,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding off the \Ncops who are on his tail
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.03,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,and making sure that you all are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.20,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:15:00.62,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Because your leader got down \Non his knees and begged us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.76,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,If you kill me, you will \Nlose their trust forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:12.09,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Given that, why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:14.67,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in\N battling to the death
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:16.78,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,with a bunch of crying fools\N standing nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:18.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,This is much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.49,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Battling to the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:22.88,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:30.94,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You're unconsciously trying to \Navoid attacking my left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.87,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of \Nthe Galaxy Sword Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Not very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:41.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That title's too flashy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You should stick to \Nbeing a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:48.79,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll figure out a way to \Nbring Obi-one back alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:52.79,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,so could you stay put and \Nnot do anything until then?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.80,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,He planted his empty head \Nright against the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.99,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.11,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:11.39,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he ask you for help
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.29,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,when he didn't say a word to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.37,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:19.16,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to keep us away \Nfrom Obi-one-niisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.79,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Obi-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.54,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody else will be joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:32.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get any \Nmore blood on your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:33.43,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:37.32,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,come back, Obi-one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:43.56,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come back and be their big \Nbrother one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:48.82,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,He was the only one who hadn't given up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.94,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,on saving Obi-one-niisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:59.41,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously believe \Nthat he's still capable
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.08,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,of returning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.80,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Come in. This is Kenofi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.05,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be picked up immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.32,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Kenofi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.53,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Kenofi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:23.48,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,We've already locked on to your \Nsignal and begun the retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.98,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Kenofi, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.89,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.57,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:51.26,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's not easy when we all \Nwork for a bunch of losers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.66,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.04,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.34,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Identify yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.60,Main01,Both,0000,0000,0000,,From the School of Tendo \NMushin Beam Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.85,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Yagyu Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.73,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,And Kondo Isami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:07.98,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,We've come here to \Nreclaim the human half...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.97,Main01,Kondo,0000,0000,0000,,...of our instructor, Obi Hajime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:19.40,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to disrupt my \Ntransmitter with that strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:22.60,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You just came here to buy time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:26.92,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,while your allies work to \Ndisable the beam cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:32.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, nobody else \Nwill be joining us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Will you leave that body first,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,or will you get rid of me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.38,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waiting game now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.89,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,Foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:49.83,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those Earth apes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:51.07,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,They tricked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.69,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,We clearly got the short \Nend of the stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.32,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck helping our rival in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:01.32,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,A victory here won't win us anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.70,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got it better \Nthan that idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.49,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,since he had to beg for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:09.92,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus he'll be losing his \Nposition as a brother figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.09,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, now I know
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.15,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,the reason why Otae-chan was able to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.59,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,smile when times were tough or painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.69,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Even if her smile isn't \Ndirected our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:29.06,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,I just want her to truly smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.06,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:35.25,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,I should laugh with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:41.91,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So people who are truly strong \Nlaugh when they want to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.29,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They endure all of the pain and sorrow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:49.48,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while laughing with everybody else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.88,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But one day, you must become \Nsamurai strong enough not to cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:03.90,Main01,Yama,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Okita, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:08.18,Image,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Image has been deleted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.18,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, big guy. I couldn't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:13.18,Main01,Oki,0000,0000,0000,,We little brothers have our own pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:16.60,Main01,Tojo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:22.71,Main01,Hiji,0000,0000,0000,,To our big brother's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:40.76,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you people are intent \Non keeping that man alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:44.26,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,But you've been wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.84,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.94,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop him at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.25,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,Not us, not him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:54.65,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,The emergency system \Nwill recover shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:59.44,Main01,Ana,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, you \NEarthlings will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.81,Main01,Kyu,0000,0000,0000,,Kondo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.40,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.21,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,That's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:06.68,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:10.83,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did he have \Nto play the bad guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.61,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he have to get \Non his knees and beg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:23.62,Main01,Kon,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give those two big brothers \Nback to Shinpachi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:29.18,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be thirty minutes \Nbefore my system recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:33.35,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way to stop the \Nbeam cannon before that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:37.76,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You have to destroy me, Obi-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:44.87,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending your little \Nbrother and this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.87,0:21:46.79,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,to see you shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:52.09,Main01,Obi,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait in hell for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.22,0:22:00.09,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call me his little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:05.30,Main01,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You people throw the word \Nbrother around too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.91,0:22:12.93,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Neither Gin-san nor I am interested \Nin being brothers, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.06,0:22:14.98,Tsuzuku,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(397,1)}To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:48.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We have a big announcement \Nabout the second movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:52.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, the censored \Nareas will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:59.87,Movie,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Gintama the Movie ----\NIn theaters on ---- ----th!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.81,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, squinting won't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:59.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If squinting helped, you'd have a lot of \Nboys spending 1/3 of their time squinting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:04.88,Ep Title,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Liquor and Gasoline\N Smiles and Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.83,0:24:01.97,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.97,0:24:04.88,Main01,Otae,0000,0000,0000,,Liquor and Gasoline, Smiles and Tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:09.34,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge atmosphere swing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.88,0:24:09.34,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,between the movie preview and \Nthe next episode preview.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:14.89,Side Bar Top,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,That's just business as usual
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:14.89,Side Bar Bottom,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,in the Gintama anime.
